;re thinking of anything below a 3, do consider raising your concerns in the respective support forum.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-2032 alignright\" title=\"WordPress\" src=\"http://i2.wp.com/ajaydsouza.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/wordpress-logo-notext-bg.png?resize=111%2C111\" alt=\"WordPress\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></a></p>\n<p>Below are a set of links of my popular plugins for you to quickly find a link to the review page.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Add to All: <a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/add-to-all/\">Plugin page</a> | <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/add-to-all\">Review page</a> | <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/plugin/add-to-all\">Support forum</a></li>\n<li>Add to Feed: <a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/add-to-feed/\">Plugin page</a> | <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/add-to-feed\">Review page</a> | <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/plugin/add-to-feed\">Support forum</a></li>\n<li>Add to Footer: <a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/add-to-footer/\">Plugin page</a> | <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/add-to-footer\">Review page</a> | <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/plugin/add-to-footer\">Support forum</a></li>\n<li>Better Search: <a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/better-search/\">Plugin page</a> | <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/better-search\">Review page</a> | <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/plugin/better-search\">Support forum</a></li>\n<li>Contextual Related Posts: <a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/contextual-related-posts/\">Plugin page</a> | <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/contextual-related-posts\">Review page</a> | <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/plugin/contextual-related-posts\">Support forum</a></li>\n<li>Top 10: <a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/wordp