F2012%2F06%2F03%2Ftwittercounter-wordpress-plugin-v1-6%2F\' data-shr_title=\'TwitterCounter+WordPress+Plugin+v1.6\'></a></div><div style=\"clear: both; min-height: 1px; height: 3px; width: 100%;\"></div><!-- End Shareaholic LikeButtonSetTop Automatic --><div class=\"KonaBody\"><p><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-2032\" title=\"WordPress\" src=\"http://i2.wp.com/ajaydsouza.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/wordpress-logo-notext-bg.png?resize=111%2C111\" alt=\"WordPress\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /> I have released v1.6 of my <a href=\"/wordpress/plugins/twittercounter/\">TwitterCounter plugin for WordPress</a>. The plugin allows you to integrate TwitterCounter.com badges on your blog to display the number of followers you have on Twitter.</p>\n<p>In addition to that you can display the TwitterCounter widget that allows you to track which twitter users are accessing your blog.</p>\n<h4>Changes in v1.6</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Modified: Plugin updated for new TwitterCounter buttons and widgets options</li>\n<li>Modified: Users now need to enter their Twitter IDs in the settings page for best results</li>\n<li>Modified: Updated WordPress widget for multiple instances</li>\n</ul>\n<p>In future versions of this plugin, I plan on adding support for basic statistics accessible via TwitterCounter API. You&#8217;ll be able to view the number of followers and predictions all within the comfort of WordPress Admin.</p>\n<p><a href=\"/wordpress/plugins/twittercounter/\">Read more &gt;</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div><div class=\"shr-publisher-2466\"></div><!-- Start Shareaholic LikeButtonSetBottom Automatic --><!-- End Shareaholic LikeButtonSetBottom Automatic --><hr style=\"border-top:black solid 1px\" /><a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2012/06/03/twittercounter-wordpress-plugin-v1-6/\">TwitterCounter WordPress Plugin v1.6</a> was first posted on June 3, 2012 at 8:46 pm.<br />© 2003-2013 \"<a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com\">Ajay - On the Road called Life</a>\". Use of this feed